      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a reliable ride for me. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has clearly been well-loved over the years. It drives smoothly and looks great\u2014perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. I\u2019ve taken care of the maintenance, so it's ready to hit the road with its next owner. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
