    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit features a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a functional variable M differential lock for superior power distribution. The high-pressure double-VANOS system has been recently serviced, ensuring the individual throttle bodies provide the signature linear power delivery and crisp induction note. The chassis remains taut with no signs of subframe fatigue, maintaining excellent lateral grip through its multi-link rear geometry. A well-maintained example that balances performance integrity with regular road use, perfect for the enthusiast seeking an authentic analog driving experience.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
