    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and reliability. The exterior retains its deep luster, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful daily use, such as small stone chips on the front bumper. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free sanctuary; the premium upholstery remains supple with minimal wear on the driver\u2019s bolster, and every electronic feature\u2014from the crisp infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014functions exactly as intended. Mechanically, this car is turn-key ready. It has benefited from a strict adherence to its maintenance schedule, including a recent full synthetic oil change and a comprehensive brake inspection. The engine pulls smoothly, and the transmission shifts are imperceptible. It comes with a clean title and a folder of service records to provide the next owner with total peace of mind. This is an honest car for a discerning buyer who values mechanical integrity and a clean aesthetic.",
      "price": 33500.0,
